If you have no Spell/Trap Cards in your Graveyard, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand), but you cannot Special Summon other monsters for the rest of this turn, except "Superheavy Samurai" monsters. If this card is Tributed for the Tribute Summon of a "Superheavy Samurai" monster while you have no Spell/Trap Cards in your Graveyard: You can Special Summon this card from your Graveyard.
